text = "Greeting Player 
Here you play as an ancient  vampire leading a cult in attempt to take over the city of [b]Respira[/b]

* Choose starting position to begin infecting the city.

* Your [b]blood[/b] represents your health, if it runs out you die a true death (game over).

* Your [b]money[/b] represents the cash your cult has at hand for you to manipulate. Your cult members are working hard to deliver this money to you.

* You can spend your money to draw [b]Influence Cards[/b].

* Each [b]Influence Cards[/b] has a benefit and a cost.

* You may hold up to three influence cards in your hand.

* The Suspicion bar represents how suspicious are the people of the city of you, the more suspicious they are the more churches(pic) they build that hinder your progress.

* In this version you can not go over district borders without using your vampiric abilities .

* Each district gives different influence cards when infected.
"
